  • Constructor Details

    • POI

      public POI(String name, String description, String layerType, int buildingID, String room, int floorID, int[] coordinates, boolean userCreated)
      POI constructor. Creates a new POI object.
      Parameters:
      name - the POI's name
      description - a short description of the POI
      layerType - the type of layer that the POI is located on
      buildingID - ID of the building that the POI is located in
      room - the room number associated with the POI
      floorID - ID of the floor that the POI is located on
      coordinates - the coordinates of the POI on the map
      userCreated - whether the POI is user created or created by admin
